comments: Bembry (ATL) makes some contact to Lillard's (POR) body but does not affect his SQBR.
Parker (ATL) jumps vertically and absorbs the oncoming body contact with Lillard (POR) during his driving shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) makes contact to Whiteside's (POR) body which affects his upward shooting motion.
Bazemore (POR) and Bembry (ATL) briefly engage and separate during the pick. The contact is deemed marginal.

Bembry (ATL) and Lillard (POR) arrive at the ball simultaneously and both players make clean contact to the ball during the rebound. Lillard's (POR) reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Bazemore (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Young's (ATL) shot attempt near the rim.
Replay review of the foul called on Lillard (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.
McCollum (POR) slightly extends his forearm into Huerter's (ATL) front but his momentum carries him away from the marginal contact.
Hezonja (POR) and Parker (ATL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Parker (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Bazemore's (POR) path when the contact occurs during the pick.
After absorbing the contact from the pick, Bazemore (POR) places a hand on the opposite side of Parker's (ATL) body but he immediately removes his hand.
Huerter (ATL) places a forearm to McCollum's (POR) front as he simultaneously dislodges the ball during the rebound. Huerter (ATL)  extends his forearm and the contact affects McCollum's SQBR.
McCollum (POR) engages and disengages with Huerter (ATL) during the rebound.
Lillard (POR) takes a legal two steps after his gather.
Jones (ATL) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) body after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (POR) and Young (ATL) briefly engage and separate off ball. The arm contact from both players is deemed marginal.
